  m_Name: Colosseum
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  answer: colosseum
  hints:
  - Despite centuries of wear and damage, ongoing restoration efforts have preserved
    this construction.
  - Known for its grand architectural design, it could hold up to 80,000 spectators
    and featured a complex system of tunnels and elevators.
  - Built during the Roman Empire, it was primarily used for gladiatorial contests
    and public spectacles.
  hintsPortuguese:
  - "Apesar de s\xE9culos de desgaste e danos, os esfor\xE7os cont\xEDnuos de restaura\xE7\xE3o
    preservaram esta constru\xE7\xE3o."
  - "Conhecido por seu grandioso projeto arquitet\xF4nico, podia acomodar at\xE9
    80.000 espectadores e contava com um complexo sistema de t\xFAneis e elevadores."
  - "Constru\xEDdo durante o Imp\xE9rio Romano, era usado principalmente para combates
    de gladiadores e espet\xE1culos p\xFAblicos."
  icon: {fileID: 2800000, guid: 8fa9f731411a66c4aba781251e00ce40, type: 3}
